long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Web client for Rugby Rush. Run the field and pass all the defenders as you rush to the try zone. Score to complete each level in this fun online rugby running game. You can collect power ups and bonuses to become stronger and get more points!
